{{Top|leg}}
The '''battleframe''' was a wearable weapons platform that operated like a personal vehicle. Though it wasn't fast or maneuverable, the battleframe could prove deadly. Providing the wearer with six mounts along the frame, each mount capable of holding weapons, ammunition, or [[Power cell/Legends|energy packs]], the battleframe transformed the wearer into a walking arsenal. At full capacity, the battleframe could support three different heavy weapons and accompanying ammo canisters or [[Blaster power pack/Legends|power packs]]. The battleframe also provided limited protection against return fire and other hazards. The market value of a battleframe was 12,000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] without any attachments or weapons. The entire unit weighed roughly 20 kilograms.

